{"tid":1322600,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"下次見到狗隻落單 唔好打 俾佢走","createTime":"2019-07-16T03:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T06:46:28.000Z","uid":37055,"like":1,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"27ecbd377d79271421aabab5ca2ff31fa95de9e9","tid":1322600,"uid":37055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:47:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wlFs0n8nkKo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwlFs0n8nkKo&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXj%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=93491820\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wlFs0n8nkKo</a><br />\n有警察被圍受傷 好似沙田俾人圍住打果個 好多中間立場雖理解但接受唔到 <br />\n最近有個phone in話柒婆想有人入浩園  意思係想有狗因公而死 無論佢係大鳩我地定點 如果真係有狗重傷 柒婆一定會煲大嚟做 到時我地就唔再屬於弱嘅一方 <br />\n我知有好多手足受傷 嚴重嘅都有 想報牛 我都想 但你要知全世界都望緊我地點樣雞蛋對高牆 係行動時分析後果 唔好衝動 死咗隻狗 真係會唔同風向<br />\n而家散仔協會已有明顯不滿 出埋聲明 俾人打嘅都係便衣 有可能係想推佢地出嚟死 <br />\n我地要推倒強權 並不是要人民vs人民 雖然佢地唔係站係我地同一陣線 亦係擋住強權面前嘅condom 但記住 我地唔好俾柒婆分化抗爭對象 <br />\n重申5大訴求 不撤不散  香港加油!"},{"pid":"ce6be5933e802ea9cca75eeed16103fe068b9c10","tid":1322600,"uid":3696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:50:09.000Z","msg":"4肢殘廢is ok 致命位唔好打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebd5feb443c3c34b4ea57d0002c1394a0c819be","tid":1322600,"uid":37055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce6be5933e802ea9cca75eeed16103fe068b9c10","tid":1322600,"uid":3696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:50:09.000Z","msg":"4肢殘廢is ok 致命位唔好打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:07:33.000Z","msg":"頭啊 心臟位啊 果啲就唔好 斷手可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a4146611cb230f7d28321255d101e2a9131a3a","tid":1322600,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:46:28.000Z","msg":"係丫 <br />\n一唔小心  打死隻狗  好大件事"}]}